type="local"
href="erct-0010.xml"
addr="erct-0010"
title="Path object">path object</fr:link></fr:title><fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon><fr:date><fr:year>2024</fr:year><fr:month>2</fr:month><fr:day>18</fr:day></fr:date><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link
type="local"
href="jonmsterling.xml"
addr="jonmsterling"
title="Jon Sterling">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:meta
name="source">
  
  
  <fr:link
type="external"
href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-0042.agda">erct-0042.agda</fr:link>
</fr:meta></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Let <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[f\colon  A\to  B]]></fr:tex> be a function equipped with a <fr:link
type="local"
href="erct-000Y.xml"
addr="erct-000Y"
title="Section-retraction pair">section</fr:link> <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\sigma  \equiv  \mathopen {}\left ({g\colon  B\to  A,\epsilon \colon  f\circ  g = 1_{B}}\right )\mathclose {}]]></fr:tex>. We can equip the <fr:link
type="local"
href="erct-0041.xml"
addr="erct-0041"
title="The coherent remainder of a section">coherent remainder</fr:link> of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\sigma ]]></fr:tex> with the structure of a <fr:link
type="local"
href="erct-0010.xml"
addr="erct-0010"
title="Path object">path object</fr:link> as follows:</fr:p><fr:ol><fr:li>
  We equip <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[g\circ  f\sim  1_{A}]]></fr:tex> with the following <fr:link
type="local"
href="erct-001C.xml"
addr="erct-001C"
title="Dependent product of path objects">dependent product</fr:link> of <fr:link
type="local"
href="erct-0013.xml"
addr="erct-0013"
title="The intrinsic path object on a type">intrinsic path object</fr:link> structures:
  <fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[    \mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\textstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}    \mathord {\vartriangle }     \mathopen {}\left ({      g\mathopen {}\left ({f x}\right )\mathclose {} = x     }\right )\mathclose {}       ]]></fr:tex></fr:li>
 <fr:li>
  For each <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\eta \colon  g\circ  f\sim 1_{A}]]></fr:tex>, we likewise equip <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {act}_{f}\circ \eta \sim  \epsilon \circ  f]]></fr:tex> with the following <fr:link
type="local"
href="erct-001C.xml"
addr="erct-001C"
title="Dependent product of path objects">dependent product</fr:link> of <fr:link
type="local"
href="erct-0013.xml"
addr="erct-0013"
title="The intrinsic path object on a type">intrinsic path object</fr:link> structures:
  <fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[    \mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\textstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}    \mathord {\vartriangle }     \mathopen {}\left ({      \mathsf {act}_{f}\mathopen {}\left ({\eta  x}\right )\mathclose {} = \epsilon \mathopen {}\left ({f x}\right )\mathclose {}     }\right )\mathclose {}       ]]></fr:tex></fr:li>
 <fr:li><fr:p>We exhibit the latter as a <fr:link
type="local"
href="erct-0032.xml"
addr="erct-0032"
title="Right cleaving of a family of path objects">right-cloven family of path objects</fr:link> over the former with the cleaving that for <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\eta _0,\eta _1\colon  g\circ  f\sim  1_{A}]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\eta _{01}\colon  \eta _0 \sim  \eta _1]]></fr:tex> defines <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\eta _{01}^*\colon  \mathsf {act}_{f}\circ \eta _1\sim  \epsilon \circ  f \to  \mathsf {act}_{f}\circ  \eta _0\sim \epsilon \circ  f]]></fr:tex> as follows:</fr:p>
  <fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[    \begin {aligned}     &\eta _{01}^*\chi  :\equiv      \lambda {x}\mathpunct {.}     \mathsf {act}_{\mathsf {act}_{f}}\mathopen {}\left ({\eta _{01}x}\right )\mathclose {}\cdot  \chi  x    \end {aligned}   ]]></fr:tex></fr:li></fr:ol><fr:p>With this cleaving in mind, finally define <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {coherentRemainder}_{f}\sigma ]]></fr:tex> to be the following <fr:link
type="local"
href="erct-0036.xml"
addr="erct-0036"
title="Contravariant sum of right-cloven families of path objects">contravariant sum</fr:link> of <fr:link
type="local"
href="erct-0010.xml"
addr="erct-0010"
title="Path object">path objects</fr:link>:</fr:p><fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[  \mathsf {coherentRemainder}_{f}\sigma  :\equiv   \mathchoice {\textstyle \int _{\mathopen {}\left ({   \eta :   \mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\textstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}   \mathord {\vartriangle }    \mathopen {}\left ({g\mathopen {}\left ({f x}\right )\mathclose {}=x}\right )\mathclose {}     }\right )\mathclose {}}}{\textstyle \int _{\mathopen {}\left ({   \eta :   \mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\textstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}   \mathord {\vartriangle }    \mathopen {}\left ({g\mathopen {}\left ({f x}\right )\mathclose {}=x}\right )\mathclose {}     }\right )\mathclose {}}}{\scriptstyle \int _{\mathopen {}\left ({   \eta :   \mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\textstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}   \mathord {\vartriangle }    \mathopen {}\left ({g\mathopen {}\left ({f x}\right )\mathclose {}=x}\right )\mathclose {}     }\right )\mathclose {}}}{\scriptscriptstyle \int _{\mathopen {}\left ({   \eta :   \mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\textstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}   \mathord {\vartriangle }    \mathopen {}\left ({g\mathopen {}\left ({f x}\right )\mathclose {}=x}\right )\mathclose {}     }\right )\mathclose {}}}  \mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\textstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}  \mathord {\vartriangle }   \mathopen {}\left ({    \mathsf {act}_{f}\mathopen {}\left ({\eta  x}\right )\mathclose {} = \epsilon \mathopen {}\left ({f x}\right )\mathclose {}   }\right )\mathclose {}   ]]></fr:tex><fr:p>Given elements <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathopen {}\left ({\eta _0,\chi _0}\right )\mathclose {}]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathopen {}\left ({\eta _1,\chi _1}\right )\mathclose {}]]></fr:tex> of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {coherentRemainder}_{f}\sigma ]]></fr:tex>, the resulting type <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathopen {}\left ({\eta _0,\chi _0}\right )\mathclose {}\cong _{\mathsf {coherentRemainder}_{f}\sigma }\mathopen {}\left ({\eta _1,\chi _1}\right )\mathclose {}]]></fr:tex> is definitionally equivalent to the following dependent sum:</fr:p><fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[  \mathchoice {\textstyle \sum _{\mathopen {}\left ({\eta _{01}:\eta _0\sim  \eta _1}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\textstyle \sum _{\mathopen {}\left ({\eta _{01}:\eta _0\sim  \eta _1}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\scriptstyle \sum _{\mathopen {}\left ({\eta _{01}:\eta _0\sim  \eta _1}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\scriptscriptstyle \sum _{\mathopen {}\left ({\eta _{01}:\eta _0\sim  \eta _1}\right )\mathclose {}}}  \chi _0 \sim  \lambda {x}\mathpunct {.} \mathsf {act}_{\mathsf {act}_{f}}\mathopen {}\left ({\eta _{01}x}\right )\mathclose {}\cdot  \chi _1 x ]]></fr:tex></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree><fr:tree
